  <brief_title>Dexmedetomidine for the Treatment of Delirium After Heart Surgery</brief_title>
  <acronym>DexinDelir</acronym>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Multi-centre, Randomised, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Comparison of Intravenous Dexmedetomidine and Haloperidol in Treatment of Psychomotor Confusion After Heart Surgery</official_title>
  <sponsors>
